    "esg_policy": {
      "value": "BlackRock Asset Management Deutschland AG integrates ESG considerations into all its active investment processes, focusing on the sustainability of investment performance over the long term. The company engages constructively with the companies it invests in to preserve clients' interests and monitor sustainability factors. It supports the promotion of sustainability in the financial sector and aligns with BlackRock's broader ESG policies, including data-driven sustainability performance metrics and principal adverse impact assessments.",
